  "date": "2025-02-04 13:00:00",
  "author": "Mariano Cocirio",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_content__xNUGz\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:24px\" data-customer-story=\"false\">\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_dateAndTimeToRead__6RnTk\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:space-between;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-6\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:6px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\"><br></p></div></div></div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">While dedicated servers provide efficiency and always-on availability, they often lead to over-provisioning, scaling challenges, and operational overhead. Serverless computing improves this with auto-scaling and pay-as-you-go pricing, but can suffer from cold starts and inefficient use of idle time.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">It’s time for a new, balanced approach. <a href=\"https://vercel.com/fluid\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\"><b>Fluid compute</b></a> evolves beyond serverless, trading single-invocation functions for high-performance mini-servers. This model has helped thousands of early adopters maximize resource efficiency, minimize cold starts, and reduce compute costs <b>by up to 85%</b>.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#what-is-fluid-compute?\" id=\"what-is-fluid-compute?\"><b>What is Fluid compute?</b>\n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Fluid compute is a new model for web application infrastructure. At its core, Fluid embraces a set of principles that optimize performance and cost while establishing a vision for meeting the demands of today’s dynamic web:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text_unorderedList__Ivoe0\">\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Compute triggers only when needed</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Real-time scaling from zero to peak traffic</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Existing resources are used before scaling new ones</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Billing based on actual compute usage, minimizing waste</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Pre-warmed instances reduce latency and prevent cold-starts</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Supports advanced tasks like streaming and post-response processing</p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">All with zero configuration and zero maintenance overhead.</p><figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\"><div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\"><div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"Fluid compute allows for more efficient compute usage than traditional serverless\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"776\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image_intrinsic__ulrJk blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media_mobile__JDB90 blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media_addPadding__2Nrnx image_lightMode__SmqSs\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3mML82dEg4xxKglQSP0Swu/649af350bc3f8e1cf4e938172914be72/traditional-serverless-vs-fluid-vercel-functions-mobile-light.png, https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3mML82dEg4xxKglQSP0Swu/649af350bc3f8e1cf4e938172914be72/traditional-serverless-vs-fluid-vercel-functions-mobile-light.png\" src=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3mML82dEg4xxKglQSP0Swu/649af350bc3f8e1cf4e938172914be72/traditional-serverless-vs-fluid-vercel-functions-mobile-light.png\">\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <figcaption class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK blog-media_caption__fNFzJ\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\">\n     Fluid compute allows for more efficient compute usage than traditional serverless\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#the-evolution-of-vercel-functions\" id=\"the-evolution-of-vercel-functions\"><b>The evolution of Vercel Functions</b>\n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Fluid delivers measurable improvements across a variety of use cases, from ecommerce to AI applications. Its unique execution model combines serverless efficiency with server-like flexibility, providing real benefits for modern web applications.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#smarter-scaling-with-higher-ceilings-and-better-cost-efficiency\" id=\"smarter-scaling-with-higher-ceilings-and-better-cost-efficiency\">Smarter scaling with higher ceilings and better cost efficiency \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Vercel Functions with Fluid compute prioritize existing resources before creating new instances, eliminating hard scaling limits and leveraging warm compute for faster, more efficient scaling. By scaling functions before instances, Fluid shifts to a <a href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/serverless-servers-node-js-with-in-function-concurrency\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">many-to-one model</a> that can handle tens of thousands of concurrent invocations.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">At the same time, Fluid mitigates the risks of uncontrolled execution that can drive up costs. Functions waiting on backend responses can process additional requests instead of sitting idle, reducing wasted compute. Built-in recursion protection prevents infinite loops before they spiral into excessive usage.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#cold-start-prevention-for-reduced-latency\" id=\"cold-start-prevention-for-reduced-latency\">Cold start prevention for reduced latency \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Fluid minimizes the effects of cold starts by greatly reducing their frequency and softening their impact. When cold starts do happen, a <a href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/vercel-functions-are-now-faster-and-powered-by-rust\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Rust-based runtime</a> with full Node.js and Python support accelerates initialization. <a href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/introducing-bytecode-caching-for-vercel-functions\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Bytecode caching</a> further speeds up invocation by pre-compiling function code, reducing startup overhead.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#support-for-advanced-tasks\" id=\"support-for-advanced-tasks\">Support for advanced tasks \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Vercel Functions with Fluid compute extend the lifecycle of an invocation, enabling function executions to extend beyond when the final response is sent back to a client.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">With <a href=\"https://vercel.com/changelog/waituntil-is-now-available-for-vercel-functions\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\"><code>waitUntil</code></a>, tasks like logging, analytics, and database updates can continue to run in the background of a compute function to reduce time to response. For AI workloads, this means managing post-response tasks like model training updates without impacting real-time performance.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#dense-global-compute-and-multi-region-failover\" id=\"dense-global-compute-and-multi-region-failover\">Dense global compute and multi-region failover \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Vercel Functions with Fluid compute support a dense global compute model, running compute closer to where your data already lives instead of attempting unrealistic replication across every edge location. Rather than forcing widespread data distribution, this approach ensures your compute is placed in regions that align with your data, optimizing for both performance and consistency.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Dynamic requests are routed to the nearest healthy compute region—among your designated locations—ensuring efficient and reliable execution. In addition to standard <a href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/effortless-high-availability-for-dynamic-frontends\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">multi-availability zone failover</a>, for enterprise customers, multi-region failover is now the default when activating Fluid.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#open,-portable,-and-fully-supported\" id=\"open,-portable,-and-fully-supported\">Open, portable, and fully supported \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Vercel Functions run without proprietary code, ensuring full portability across any provider that supports standard function execution. Developers don’t need to write functions explicitly for the infrastructure—workloads are inferred and automatically provisioned.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">With full Node.js and Python runtime support, including native modules and the standard library, Fluid ensures seamless compatibility with existing applications and frameworks—without runtime constraints.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#enable-fluid-compute-on-vercel-today\" id=\"enable-fluid-compute-on-vercel-today\">Enable Fluid compute on Vercel today \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Fluid compute is available for all users today. Go to the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%5Bproject%5D%2Fsettings%2Ffunctions\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Functions tab</a> in your Project Settings to activate—no migrations or application code changes required.<a class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_wrapper__TDjPR\" data-version=\"v1\" href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/fluid-compute#how-to-enable-fluid-compute\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255 255 255/var(--tw-bg-opacity,1)); font-family: var(--font-sans),ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif,&quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;,&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,&quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; --stack-flex: initial; --stack-direction: column; --stack-align: center; --stack-justify: flex-start; --stack-padding: 0px; --stack-gap: 0px;\"></a></p><div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_content___HJjb\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex: initial; --sm-stack-direction: column; --md-stack-direction: row; --stack-align: stretch; --stack-justify: flex-start; --stack-padding: 0px; --sm-stack-gap: 16px; --md-stack-gap: 24px; --lg-stack-gap: 24px; --xl-stack-gap: 24px; display: inline !important;\"><div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex: initial; --stack-direction: column; --stack-align: stretch; --stack-justify: flex-start; --stack-padding: 0px; --stack-gap: 4px; display: inline !important;\"><p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK inline-cta_text__5aH50\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color: var(--ds-gray-900); --text-size: 1rem; --text-line-height: 1.5rem; --text-letter-spacing: initial; --text-weight: 400; display: inline !important;\"><strong>Enable Fluid compute today</strong></p></div></div><a class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_wrapper__TDjPR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\" href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/fluid-compute#how-to-enable-fluid-compute\"><div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_content___HJjb\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--sm-stack-direction:column;--md-stack-direction:row;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--sm-stack-gap:16px;--md-stack-gap:24px;--lg-stack-gap:24px;--xl-stack-gap:24px\"><div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:4px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:1rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\">Fluid is our fast, cost-efficient compute, available today.</p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:flex-start;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK inline-cta_cta__uN1sr\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:500\">Enable Now</p>\n     </div>\n    </div></a>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">After Fluid is enabled, you can monitor your performance in the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%5Bproject%5D%2Fobservability\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Observability tab</a> to track metrics like function performance and compute savings.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Learn more in the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/changelog/vercel-functions-can-now-run-on-fluid-compute\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">changelog</a> and <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/fluid-compute\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">documentation</a>.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><i>Acknowledgments: While Fluid is a new compute model, it builds on previous work in the community. We'd like to acknowledge products like Google Cloud Run, and other autoscaling server infrastructure, which has approached solving these problems in similar ways.</i></p>\n  </div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 的灵活计算通过优化资源效率、可扩展性和成本效益，重新定义了无服务器计算，减少了冷启动并提升了性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 的灵活计算通过优化资源效率、可扩展性和成本效益，重新定义了无服务器计算，减少了冷启动并提升了性能。",
  "summary": "灵活计算是 Vercel 推出的一项创新基础设施解决方案，旨在解决传统无服务器计算的挑战。它通过优先使用现有资源而非扩展新实例来提高效率，实现实时扩展并减少与冷启动相关的延迟。灵活计算通过优化计算使用和最小化浪费，提供成本节约，潜在降低计算成本高达 85%。该模型支持高级用例，包括 AI 工作负载、后台处理和多区域故障转移的全球计算，同时确保零配置和维护开销。专为现代 Web 应用程序设计，灵活计算实现了无缝的可移植性和灵活性，避免了供应商锁定，并与 Node.js 和 Python 运行时兼容。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "灵活计算通过优先使用现有资源而非创建新实例来优化扩展。",
      "explanation": "这种方法通过优先使用现有计算容量而非部署额外资源，确保更高效的资源使用，降低扩展成本并提升性能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "灵活计算显著减少了冷启动，改善了延迟和用户体验。",
      "explanation": "通过最小化冷启动的发生并使用基于 Rust 的运行时，灵活计算加速了初始化时间，同时字节码缓存进一步减少了调用开销。"
    },
    {
      "point": "灵活计算支持高级任务和扩展调用，以实现更好的响应后处理。",
      "explanation": "灵活计算支持后台任务，例如日志记录或 AI 模型更新，在主响应交付后运行，确保资源的高效使用和无缝的实时性能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "灵活计算的密集全球计算模型通过将计算资源放置在更靠近数据源的位置，优化了性能和一致性。",
      "explanation": "这确保了更快、更可靠的执行，因为计算资源靠近数据源，并且可以在多个区域之间无缝故障转移。"
    },
    {
      "point": "灵活计算是开放的、可移植的，并与标准函数执行兼容，避免了供应商锁定。",
      "explanation": "灵活计算的开放、非专有设计允许开发者使用现有应用程序和框架，只需进行最小更改，促进了跨云提供商的可移植性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "灵活计算将计算成本降低高达 85%，在无服务器和传统基于服务器的模型之间提供了平衡的方法。",
    "灵活计算通过预热实例并使用基于 Rust 的运行时加速函数初始化，最小化了冷启动。",
    "借助灵活计算，开发者可以实时从零到峰值扩展，而无需担心过度配置或浪费。",
    "灵活计算的密集全球计算通过将资源放置在更靠近数据源的位置，确保了更可靠的性能，优化了速度和一致性。",
    "灵活计算的开放和可移植设计允许与现有框架无缝集成，确保灵活性而无需供应商锁定。"
  ],
